                            <comment id="14479053" author="paulk" created="Fri, 9 Apr 2010 12:09:50 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Just added a few tweaks to handle some of the really simple cases.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Maps detect themselves as top level value (already there - just aligned syntax with Java):&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;code panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;codeContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre class=&quot;code-java&quot;&gt;def m = [a:1]
m.self = m
&lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;assert&lt;/span&gt; m.toMapString() == &lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&apos;[a:1, self:(&lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;this&lt;/span&gt; Map)]&apos;&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Ditto for list (again using Java syntax):&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;code panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;codeContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre class=&quot;code-java&quot;&gt;def l = [&lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&apos;first&apos;&lt;/span&gt;]
l &amp;lt;&amp;lt; l
&lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;assert&lt;/span&gt; l.toListString() == &lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&apos;[first, (&lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;this&lt;/span&gt; Collection)]&apos;&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;p&gt;In addition, if you call &lt;tt&gt;toListString()&lt;/tt&gt; or &lt;tt&gt;toMapString()&lt;/tt&gt; directly you can supply a max size param.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;code panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;codeContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre class=&quot;code-java&quot;&gt;def animals = [&lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&apos;ant&apos;&lt;/span&gt;, &lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&apos;bee&apos;&lt;/span&gt;, &lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&apos;cat&apos;&lt;/span&gt;]
animals &amp;lt;&amp;lt; [pets:animals]
&lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;assert&lt;/span&gt; animals.toListString(5)  == &lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&apos;[ant, ...]&apos;&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;assert&lt;/span&gt; animals.toListString(10) == &lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&apos;[ant, bee, ...]&apos;&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;assert&lt;/span&gt; animals.toListString(15) == &lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&apos;[ant, bee, cat, ...]&apos;&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;assert&lt;/span&gt; animals.toListString(20) == &lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&apos;[ant, bee, cat, [pets:[...]]]&apos;&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;assert&lt;/span&gt; animals.toListString(40) == &lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&apos;[ant, bee, cat, [pets:[ant, bee, cat, [pets:[...]]]]]&apos;&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The size param isn&apos;t hooked up to any &lt;tt&gt;toString()&lt;/tt&gt; methods by default as that might break existing code.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
